No Democratic-led Senate coalition can reach a majority. [? if non_dem_senate_has_majority = 1 : The largest viable non-Democratic Senate bloc organizes the chamber: ?][? if non_dem_senate_has_majority = 0 : No non-Democratic bloc can organize the Senate either; the chamber is deadlocked around the largest possible bloc: ?]

