go-to: ministries

Rainey's selection as Speaker is approved by our potential allies.

@braun
title: John Nance Garner for Speaker
view-if: not historical_mode or not spd_prussia
subtitle: Garner can reassure conservatives, but labor and New Deal liberals will demand procedural concessions.

Farmer-Labor has significant qualms about putting Garner in charge of the House coalition, given his hostility to aggressive redistribution. They ask for procedural concessions in exchange.

- @muller
- @wels
- @braun_2: Let Farmer-Labor have procedural concessions.

@braun_2
subtitle: John Nance Garner will be Speaker.
